OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776665107
OL,3,CStarmer urged to publish advice given
OL,4,Con Mandelson ahead of 'judgement day'
OL,6,FA due diligence assessment prepared by
OL,7,Fthe Cabinet Office propriety and
OL,8,Fethics team before the Labour peer was
OL,9,Fsent to Washington flagged his links
OL,10,Fto US paedophile financier Jeffrey
OL,11,FEpstein.
OL,13,FThe Foreign Office then conducted
OL,14,Fdeveloped vetting on Lord Mandelson,
OL,15,Fbut despite officials recommending
OL,16,Fthat the former MP should not be given
OL,17,Fthe appointment, it went ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
