OL,3,CStarmer urged to publish advice given
OL,4,Con Mandelson ahead of 'judgement day'
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat Leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,7,Fsaid on Saturday: "Keir Starmer needs
OL,8,Fto come clean and publish the initial
OL,9,Fdue diligence report carried out on
OL,10,FPeter Mandelson before he was
OL,11,Fappointed.
OL,13,F"No more ministers hiding behind
OL,14,Fprocess and dragging their feet, the
OL,15,Fpublic deserve full transparency now.
OL,17,F"We need to know exactly what concerns
OL,18,Fthe Prime Minister decided to ignore,
OL,19,Fand why, before he updates the Commons
OL,20,Fon Monday."
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@AOUyD@AOU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
