OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1776665107
OL,3,CStarmer urged to publish advice given
OL,4,Con Mandelson ahead of 'judgement day'
OL,6,F"This was clearly a catastrophic error
OL,7,Fthat has put our national security at
OL,8,Frisk. Chucking civil servants under
OL,9,Fthe bus isn't good enough, the Prime
OL,10,FMinister needs to take responsibility
OL,11,Ffor his own actions."
OL,13,FThe Foreign Office's chief civil
OL,14,Fservant, Sir Olly Robbins, was sacked
OL,15,Fon Thursday night after Sir Keir and
OL,16,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper lost
OL,17,Fconfidence in him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@UO]
