OL,3,CStarmer urged to publish advice given
OL,4,Con Mandelson ahead of 'judgement day'
OL,6,FWriting on X, she said: "Keir Starmer
OL,7,Fhas now sacked everyone involved in
OL,8,FMandelson's appointment - Chris
OL,9,FWormald, Morgan McSweeney, Olly
OL,10,FRobbins.But Starmer was ultimately the
OL,11,Fone who approved it. He's got no one
OL,12,Fleft to sack. It's time for him to
OL,13,Ftake responsibility. He should go."
