OL,3,CStarmer urged to publish advice given
OL,4,Con Mandelson ahead of 'judgement day'
OL,6,FShe later wrote: "The prime minister
OL,7,Fis taking us for fools. He said today
OL,8,Fthat no one in Number 10 knew."On the
OL,9,F12 of September, the FRONT PAGE of the
OL,10,FIndependent clearly states that 'MI6
OL,11,Ffailed to clear' Mandelson. He wants
OL,12,Fus to believe no one thought to check?
OL,13,FIt's utterly absurd."
